This is a WordPress Plugin project.
Thanks:Advanced Custom Fields

部署方法
==================
api=>document_root/api
custom-avatar=>document_root/wp-content/plugins/custom-avatar
sakuratya=>document_root/wp-content/plugins/sakuratya
theme=>document_root/wp-content/themes/sakuratya
MySQL运行：
CREATE TABLE `wp_favorites` (
  `user_id` bigint(20) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `post_id` bigint(20) unsigned NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`user_id`,`post_id`)
);